Package: TestAnaAPP
Title: The shiny app for test analysis and visualization
Version: 0.1.2
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Youxiang", family = "Jiang", 
    email = "jiangyouxiang34@163.com", 
    role = c("cre", "aut"),
    comment = "0000-0003-4557-5038"),
    person(given = "Hongbo", family = "Wen", 
