Description: This application can realize exploratory factor analysis,
    confirmatory factor analysis, classical measurement theory analysis,
    single and multi-dimensional item response theory analysis through the
    shiny interactive interface, and realize the visualization of the
    results. The analysis results are easily downloaded in the interactive
    interface. At the same time, users can also download a brief project
    reaction theory analysis report on the interactive interface.
